{
  "id": "RAW_fc09f6",
  "title": "DeepSeek V3 深夜低调升级，代码进化令人震惊，网友实测可媲美 Claude 3.5/3.7 Sonnet",
  "url": "https://www.jiqizhixin.com/articles/2025-03-25-4",
  "date": "2025-03-25 02:32:36",
  "author": "机器之心",
  "siteName": "机器之心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section>\n   昨夜，DeepSeek V3 毫无征兆地来了一波更新，升级到了「DeepSeek-V3-0324」版本。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   目前，新版本在 Hugging Face 上可以下载并部署。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503477909\" data-ratio=\"0.44074074074074077\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a7219a17-4b88-4332-c7a3-946e2e8d8900/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"1\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/671a3a58-69a0-42d4-918b-9a3e669faa62/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"0\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <ul>\n   <li>\n    <p>Hugging Face 地址：https://huggingface.co/deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V3-0324/tree/main</p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section>\n   不过，DeepSeek-V3-0324 没有公布详细的模型卡。我们只能看到它的参数为 6850 亿以及张量类型。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503477910\" data-ratio=\"0.16203703703703703\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bd9c635d-b071-4ce0-6d69-3136734da000/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"2\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/8017a370-8c66-41d3-9d7d-0b06bbf1a336/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"1\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   此外，DeepSeek-V3-0324 支持了更宽松的 MIT 开源协议。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503477911\" data-ratio=\"0.1388888888888889\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/dca48c79-84cb-408b-10cc-25dc45380f00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"3\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/c6becb0f-ac98-43a0-b802-b60e2188b13c/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"2\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   模型放出来后，DeepSeek-V3-0324 的代码能力让所有人震惊了！\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   有人表示，经过自己的测试，DeepSeek-V3-0324 在数学推理和前端开发方面的表现优于 Claude 3.5 和 Claude 3.7 Sonnet。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503477912\" data-ratio=\"0.8574074074074074\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2f5de648-5527-4b62-d097-d1e68eecd600/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"4\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/00c0d66a-ea0c-444f-a58e-9b9b74786151/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"3\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 50%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <em><sup>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 图源：https://x.com/selcukemiravci/status/1904311856313028870</sup></em>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   X 博主「@KuittinenPetri」表示，Anthropic 和 OpenAI 陷入了困境。更新后的 DeepSeek-V3-0324 可以轻松免费地创建漂亮的 HTML5、CSS 和前端。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503477913\" data-ratio=\"0.887962962962963\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b0fa2096-814d-4423-0519-9bb6a38f5a00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"5\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/acafea83-4732-41f6-ba9e-d09fc171aad0/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"4\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 50%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <em><sup>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 图源：https://x.com/KuittinenPetri/status/1904224441384771909</sup></em>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   提示词如下：为 AI 公司「NexusAI」创建一个外观精美的响应式首页，将所有内容包含在一个 HTML5 文件中。结果如下图所示，所有图像，包括用户故事和他们的面孔，一切都是用这个提示完成的。&nbsp;\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   他认为：<strong>DeepSeek-V3-0324 是 DeepSeek 最好的非推理模型，通常更适合创意写作任务，但现在也比 R1 更适合制作 HTML5 + CSS + 前端</strong>。上述提示的结果代码总共 958 行，但它实际上实现了一个交互式网站，包括所有图像。并且结果也适用于移动设备。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"图片编辑助手-2025325-1742857521294.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503477929\" data-ratio=\"0.2814814814814815\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ee1e8433-ec5a-4f28-5dbf-ff48c0b3fd00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"6\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/02e124b9-dff2-43f6-8945-2e28c2c72d09/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"5\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"图片编辑助手-2025325-1742857573047.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503477914\" data-ratio=\"0.2814814814814815\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a4fd0176-e0bd-476c-8932-1d8a16752000/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"7\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/c26b34ca-18f6-40f8-a0dc-00114aa95d47/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"6\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   他还称，DeepSeek-V3-0324 在编写代码方面确实很棒！早期测试显示，它是所有开源选择中最好的非推理模型，甚至可以与 Claude 3.5/3.7 Sonnet 相媲美。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503477915\" data-ratio=\"0.23148148148148148\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0d46fb89-fa81-45b9-8389-753b0d9e4d00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"8\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/386712fb-adc8-4fa1-8a06-bb5e4ae902be/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"7\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   另一位网友也让 DeepSeek-V3-0324 创建网站，只见该模型一口气写了 800 多行代码，中途一次都没卡壳，生成的网站布局也非常完美。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503477916\" data-ratio=\"0.5110375275938189\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8cbe4ed2-4052-40a2-3d4c-8b16c7bfef00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"906\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"9\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/fb921139-8ab9-47b7-bf0b-a6c44391d5ca/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"8\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-imgfileid=\"503477917\" data-ratio=\"0.56875\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b09f370f-1b0d-44f2-ba5c-6172d0232100/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" data-original-style=\"\" data-index=\"10\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/66eb0550-42f5-4268-ab6b-8ecfa1d62c66/640.gif\" data-order=\"0\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"9\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   这位网友还把提示语放出来了，简单的几行字，大家可以前去一试。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503477918\" data-ratio=\"0.6581005586592179\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7f8d4546-d202-4d86-76d9-3e8fd2eda000/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"895\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"11\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/541e6792-6156-4e78-a7b8-23a4a1fb2779/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"10\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   Hyperbolic 联合创始人兼 CTO Yuchen 称自己的氛围测试显示，DeepSeek- V3-0324 已经有了一些思维链模型的影子。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   他测试了题目「strawberry 中有多少个 r」，可以看到，DeepSeek-V3-0324 展示了详细的推理步骤。他表示，真正的「Open AI」又赢了。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503477919\" data-ratio=\"0.4925925925925926\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/92db0135-5a58-4f27-695a-fa47b1caa400/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"12\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/51b01681-4a96-4c62-b722-53da2089be13/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"11\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-imgfileid=\"503477930\" data-ratio=\"0.5609756097560976\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9d34d3e0-2f6b-4a9f-cc86-87c551cc0900/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"738\" data-original-style=\"\" data-index=\"13\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/fb286585-ed35-49bb-9982-b3e57d999e0c/640.gif\" data-order=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"13\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <em><sup>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;图源：https://x.com/Yuchenj_UW/status/1904223627509465116</sup></em>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   还有人将 DeepSeek-V3-0324 与 OpenAI o1-pro 生成小球的效果进行了比较。下面是 o1-pro 的效果：\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-imgfileid=\"503477923\" data-ratio=\"0.975\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f56e77eb-d6ce-4b0b-14d7-65329ad4f000/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" data-original-style=\"\" data-index=\"14\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/b47e55a8-7af0-4f02-9554-771758112e1e/640.gif\" data-order=\"2\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"16\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 50%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   他表示，DeepSeek-V3-0324 大约可以实现 o1-pro70% 的性能，但它免费并且 API 价格比后者便宜了至少 50 倍。二者选谁一目了然！\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-imgfileid=\"503477922\" data-ratio=\"1.1140625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0dfa34f7-4ace-4834-17cb-3d4ad8c78700/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" data-original-style=\"\" data-index=\"15\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/570b37ba-fe6c-4946-9a27-37eca47e56da/640.gif\" data-order=\"3\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"12\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <em><sup>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 图源：https://x.com/michaelkaoi/status/1904178015833297342</sup></em>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   X 博主「orange.ai」对 DeepSeek V3、DeepSeek-V3-0324 与 Claude Sonnet 3.7 的海报设计结果进行了比较，同样表示前端代码能力相比上代有了显著增强。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503477920\" data-ratio=\"0.4398148148148148\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c0533bfa-6508-415b-0a15-31416ce32d00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"16\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/3b1dabbd-00bb-4d65-92e5-bb43e95ecbf1/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"14\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"图片编辑助手-2025325-1742859951676.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503477921\" data-ratio=\"0.4111111111111111\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2948b2d6-154c-4fc3-041c-2c2dc53cea00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"17\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/3de9400f-b9ed-4be7-9f45-af52d09d0bc2/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"15\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <em><sup>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 图源：https://x.com/oran_ge/status/1904306405823467526</sup></em>\n  </section>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "DeepSeek V3 深夜升级至 0324 版本，代码能力显著提升，网友测评在数学推理和前端开发方面可媲美 Claude 3.5/3.7 Sonnet。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "DeepSeek V3 深夜升级至 0324 版本，代码能力显著提升，网友测评在数学推理和前端开发方面可媲美 Claude 3.5/3.7 Sonnet。",
  "summary": "DeepSeek V3 在 3 月 24 日进行了版本更新，发布了 DeepSeek-V3-0324 模型。该模型参数为 6850 亿，并采用了更宽松的 MIT 开源协议。模型一经发布，其代码能力便引起了广泛关注。多位网友的测试表明，DeepSeek-V3-0324 在数学推理和前端开发方面的表现甚至优于 Claude 3.5 和 Claude 3.7 Sonnet。尤其是在 HTML5、CSS 和前端代码生成方面，DeepSeek-V3-0324 表现出色，能够以较少的提示词快速生成高质量、响应式的网页代码。此外，还有测评显示，DeepSeek-V3-0324 在某些任务上可以达到 OpenAI o1-pro 70% 的性能，但 API 价格却便宜很多。综合来看，DeepSeek-V3-0324 在代码生成和推理能力上都有了显著提升，是一款极具竞争力的开源大语言模型。",
